    ffv1dec: check that global parameters dont change in version 0/1
    
    Such changes are not allowed nor supported
    
    Fixes Ticket2906
    
    Found-by: ami_stuff
    Signed-off-by: Michael Niedermayer <michaelni@gmx.at>

